name: JS BloggerPress
body:
# Welcome to JS BloggerPress #
All the files required to run the Bloggerpress template created by [Insight](http://www.be-insight.com/) is stored here. Original codes were hosted at <https://code.google.com/p/jsbloggerpress/>

## BloggerPress ##
The BloggerPress theme download is available here: <http://btemplates.com/2009/blogger-template-bloggerpress/>

## Live Example ##
A live example of BloggerPress and how you can link your JavaScript files can be found here: http://www.2pmkoreanband.com
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
